Our rewarding structure has been flexibly designed to provide contributors with valuable tokens which can be instantly converted to fiat currency on any crypto exchange. Each step of our economic model is designed in a way that will make everyone in the community happy and current models in the ecosystem all feed on each other, creating demand while also feeding everybody.
